---
import PageLayout from '@layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="Features — Mentric Coaching Platform" description="Explore the full Mentric feature set: session management, goals, assessments, 360 feedback, analytics, CPD tracking, AI assistant, and more.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-glow-gradient">
    <div class="section-container py-10 md:py-14 text-center">
      <p class="category-label mb-4">Platform</p>
      <h1 class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        Everything you need to run a
        <span class="text-primary">world-class coaching practice</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg md:text-xl">
        From session scheduling to 360 feedback, CPD tracking to AI-powered insights
        — Mentric brings every tool a modern coaching practice needs into one
        beautifully designed platform.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Session Management -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="section-container py-14 md:py-20">
      <p class="category-label mb-3">Sessions</p>
      <h2 class="max-w-3xl">Session Management</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg">
        Schedule, run, and review coaching sessions across every format — with
        intelligent tools that capture what matters so you can focus on the
        conversation.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <img src="/images/sessions.webp" alt="Mentric session management interface showing scheduled coaching sessions with status, format, and attendee details" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-editorial-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Multi-format scheduling</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Schedule sessions across Zoom, Microsoft Teams, phone, and in-person
            — all from one calendar view.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Notes, actions &amp; outcomes</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Capture session notes in real time, assign follow-up actions, and
            record outcomes linked to goals.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">AI summaries &amp; transcription</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Automatic session summaries and full transcription powered by
            Fireflies integration — never miss a key insight.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Group coaching sessions</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Run group sessions with full attendance tracking, individual notes,
            and post-session follow-ups for each participant.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">RSVP &amp; calendar management</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Coachees confirm attendance directly. Calendar invitations sync
            automatically so everyone stays aligned.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Goals & Journeys -->
  <section class="bg-background">
    <div class="section-container py-14 md:py-20">
      <p class="category-label mb-3">Progress</p>
      <h2 class="max-w-3xl">Goals &amp; Journeys</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg">
        Structure coaching engagements around meaningful goals and visual
        journeys that track real progress — from first awareness through to
        lasting integration.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <img src="/images/goals-pipeline.webp" alt="Goals pipeline view showing coachee progress across coaching journey stages in a kanban-style board" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-editorial-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Customisable coaching journeys</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Create structured journeys with configurable stages — Awareness,
            Development, Mastery, Integration — tailored to each coachee.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Milestones &amp; due dates</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Set goals with clear milestones, target dates, and evidence
            requirements to keep coaching on track.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Evidence tracking</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Upload evidence files or link external proof — deployed projects,
            published articles, certifications — to demonstrate real-world impact.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">AI goal recommendations</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Let Mentric's AI suggest personalised goals based on assessment
            results, saving time and surfacing blindspots.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Visual pipeline view</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            See every coachee's progress at a glance with a kanban-style pipeline
            that shows where they are in their journey.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Configurable ownership</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Choose whether goals are coach-led or coachee-led — empowering
            self-directed development or maintaining structured guidance.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Assessments & 360 Feedback -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="section-container py-14 md:py-20">
      <p class="category-label mb-3">Measurement</p>
      <h2 class="max-w-3xl">Assessments &amp; 360 Feedback</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg">
        Build bespoke assessments, gather multi-rater feedback, and track scores
        over time to measure genuine behavioural change.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <img src="/images/assessments.webp" alt="Assessments page showing assessment templates, 360 feedback assignments, and score tracking" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-editorial-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Custom assessment templates</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Build assessments with 8+ question types — scale, multiple choice,
            rating, ranking, matrix Likert, free text, true/false, and more.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">360-degree feedback</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Gather multi-rater feedback from managers, peers, and reports with
            full respondent tracking and anonymity controls.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">AI question generation</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Generate targeted assessment questions with AI, focused on specific
            competencies or development areas.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Score trends</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Track scores across repeated assessments to visualise growth and
            identify areas that need attention.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Competency frameworks</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Integrate your organisation's competency framework so assessment
            results map directly to the behaviours that matter.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Scheduled &amp; recurring</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Set assessments to repeat on a schedule — monthly, quarterly, or
            custom — so measurement happens consistently.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Resources & Learning -->
  <section class="bg-background">
    <div class="section-container py-14 md:py-20">
      <p class="category-label mb-3">Knowledge</p>
      <h2 class="max-w-3xl">Resources &amp; Learning</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg">
        Build and share curated resource libraries to support coaching
        engagements — from articles and frameworks to videos and worksheets.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <img src="/images/resources.webp" alt="Resources library showing curated coaching materials organised by category with sharing controls" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-editorial-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Personal &amp; organisation libraries</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Maintain your own resource library alongside organisation-level
            shared collections for consistency across your practice.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Individual &amp; bulk sharing</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Share resources with individual coachees or in bulk across a
            programme — with full control over timing and visibility.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Engagement tracking</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            See who has viewed, downloaded, or engaged with shared resources
            to understand what resonates.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Multi-format support</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Upload documents, videos, links, and articles — everything your
            coachees need in one searchable place.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Analytics & Insights -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="section-container py-14 md:py-20">
      <p class="category-label mb-3">Intelligence</p>
      <h2 class="max-w-3xl">Analytics &amp; Insights</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg">
        Role-based dashboards and AI-powered queries that turn coaching data into
        actionable insight — for coaches, coachees, and organisations alike.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <img src="/images/analytics.webp" alt="Analytics dashboard displaying coaching engagement metrics, trend charts, and programme performance data" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-editorial-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Role-based dashboards</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Coaches, admins, and coachees each get a tailored dashboard showing
            the metrics that matter most to their role.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Trends &amp; engagement metrics</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Trend charts, engagement scores, and status summaries that reveal
            patterns across your entire practice.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">AI natural language queries</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Ask questions in plain English — "Which coachees haven't had a session
            in 30 days?" — and get instant, data-backed answers.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Assessment &amp; 360 comparisons</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Compare assessment score trends over time and view 360 feedback
            side-by-side to spot real behavioural shifts.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Programme comparison</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Organisations can benchmark coaching programmes against each other
            to understand what drives the best outcomes.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Export &amp; reporting</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Export data and generate reports for stakeholder presentations, board
            reviews, or accreditation submissions.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CPD & Accreditation -->
  <section class="bg-background">
    <div class="section-container py-14 md:py-20">
      <p class="category-label mb-3">Professional Development</p>
      <h2 class="max-w-3xl">CPD &amp; Accreditation</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg">
        Track your continuing professional development effortlessly — from
        automatic session logging to reflective practice and accreditation
        evidence.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <img src="/images/cpd.webp" alt="CPD tracking dashboard showing coaching hours, supervision records, and accreditation progress" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-editorial-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Automatic hours logging</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Coaching session hours are logged automatically — no double entry,
            no spreadsheets, no guesswork.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Manual CPD &amp; supervision hours</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Record CPD activities, supervision sessions, and other professional
            development hours alongside your coaching work.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Reflective practice journal</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Maintain a structured reflective journal that supports your
            professional growth and accreditation requirements.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Accreditation evidence</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Link evidence directly to accreditation requirements — hours,
            reflections, supervision records — all in one place.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">CPD dashboard</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            A clear dashboard showing total coaching hours, CPD activities, and
            supervision metrics against your targets.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Messaging & Collaboration -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="section-container py-14 md:py-20">
      <p class="category-label mb-3">Communication</p>
      <h2 class="max-w-3xl">Messaging &amp; Collaboration</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg">
        Keep coaching conversations flowing between sessions with built-in
        messaging, file sharing, and real-time notifications.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <img src="/images/messages.webp" alt="In-platform messaging interface showing coach-coachee conversations with file sharing" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-editorial-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Direct messaging</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Secure, in-platform messaging between coaches and coachees — no need
            to switch to email or external apps.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Group conversations</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Start group threads for cohort discussions, programme announcements,
            or peer support circles.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">File &amp; link sharing</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Share documents, links, and resources directly within conversations
            for easy reference.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Real-time notifications</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Instant notifications powered by SignalR keep everyone informed
            the moment something needs their attention.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Group Coaching -->
  <section class="bg-background">
    <div class="section-container py-14 md:py-20">
      <p class="category-label mb-3">Groups</p>
      <h2 class="max-w-3xl">Group Coaching</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg">
        Manage group coaching engagements with the same rigour as one-to-one
        — from group creation and scheduling through to individual attendance
        and dynamics tracking.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <img src="/images/command-center.webp" alt="Coach command center showing group management with participant lists and session scheduling" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-editorial-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Flexible group creation</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Create coaching groups defined by the coach or drawn from a
            programme's participant list — whichever suits your model.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Group session scheduling</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Schedule sessions for multiple attendees with a single booking,
            including calendar invitations for every participant.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Individual attendance tracking</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Record attendance per participant — Attended, No-Show, Excused, or
            Partial — for accurate reporting.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">RSVP management</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Participants RSVP to group sessions so you know exactly who to
            expect before the session begins.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Group dynamics notes</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Capture observations about group dynamics, themes, and interactions
            alongside individual participant notes.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- AI Assistant -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="section-container py-14 md:py-20">
      <p class="category-label mb-3">Artificial Intelligence</p>
      <h2 class="max-w-3xl">AI Assistant</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg">
        An intelligent assistant woven throughout the platform — answering
        questions about your coaching data, generating suggestions, and
        automating the tasks that slow you down.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <img src="/images/analytics.webp" alt="AI-powered analytics showing natural language query results and intelligent coaching insights" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-editorial-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Natural language queries</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Ask questions about your coaching data in everyday language and
            receive clear, accurate answers instantly.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Goal suggestions</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            AI analyses assessment results and recommends personalised goals
            — giving you a head start on development planning.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Automatic milestone creation</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Once a goal is set, the AI can suggest a breakdown of milestones
            to make progress measurable and achievable.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Session summary generation</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Get concise, structured summaries of coaching sessions — capturing
            key themes, decisions, and next steps.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Assessment question generation</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Generate assessment questions targeted at specific competencies,
            saving hours of manual assessment design.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Branding & White-Label -->
  <section class="bg-background">
    <div class="section-container py-14 md:py-20">
      <p class="category-label mb-3">Customisation</p>
      <h2 class="max-w-3xl">Branding &amp; White-Label</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg">
        Make Mentric your own. Apply your logo, colours, and fonts so the
        platform feels like a seamless extension of your coaching brand.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <img src="/images/settings-branding.webp" alt="Branding settings page showing logo upload, colour picker, font selection, and live theme preview" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-editorial-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Custom logo, colours &amp; fonts</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Upload your logo and set your brand colours and typography to create
            a fully branded experience.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Per-client branding</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
            Practice organisations can apply different branding for each client,
            delivering a tailored experience to every engagement.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-5 py-1">
